    "body": "## Summary\n- realign legacy Alpha aggregate expectations to the current accepted inventory: 174 entries / 152 unique / 206 allowed\n- preserve the original 23-row Z-to-Alpha cohort while treating later respect coverage as additive\n- update Alpha New Features expectations to 8 groups / 83 rows / 66 changed / 17 identity / respect 10\n- remove mutable TASKS.md and PROJECT_MEMORY.md from docs-acceptance identity while preserving deterministic Alpha document integrity checks\n- refresh mirrored dev-check cache-bust only; no product runtime semantics changed\n\n## Scope\nExactly 10 changed paths, all within the authorized 12-path task scope. No data.js, system.js, gameplay, economy, NPC, persistence, state, handler, or production-runtime behavior changes.\n\n## Validation\n- selector authorization: <redacted>\n- node --check on both dev-check mirrors: PASS\n- source/docs mirror parity: PASS for all five changed mirror pairs\n- legacy child smokes: 5/5 PASS\n- aggregate Alpha legacy smoke: PASS with 174 / 152 / 206, taboo 60, Z cohort 23/23/100%, New Features 8/83\n- docs acceptance smokes: PASS\n- git diff --check: PASS\n- Safari runtime was not run and is not claimed\n\nReviewed implementation head: `0928e367de57a6769d99e2206c6f86b7072302ff`\nBase main at review: `88b5cf6dbe4d4db76187aca3b6baaa3e2a4d6108`",
